trans-unit.source: Represents a wrapper used to establish link between an actual <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Presentation.ToolboxItem" /> instance and the tool representation, as well as add support for categorization of toolbox items.
trans-unit.target: 실제 <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Presentation.ToolboxItem" /> 인스턴스와 도구 표현 간의 연결을 설정하고 도구 상자 항목의 분류를 위한 지원을 추가하는 래퍼를 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: This class is <see langword="sealed" />, so it cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 이 클래스는 <see langword="sealed" />되므로 상속할 수 없습니다.

trans-unit.source: This wrapper class provides support for the categorization of toolbox items when re-hosting the [!INCLUDE[wfd1](~/includes/wfd1-md.md)]outside of [!INCLUDE[vs2010](~/includes/vs2010-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: 이 래퍼는 [!INCLUDE[wfd1](~/includes/wfd1-md.md)]외부에서 [!INCLUDE[vs2010](~/includes/vs2010-md.md)]를 다시 호스팅할 때 도구 상자 항목의 분류를 위한 지원을 제공합니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper" /> class.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper" /> class.

The default constructor initializes the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper.ToolName%2A>, <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper.AssemblyName%2A>, <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper.BitmapName%2A>, and <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper.DisplayName%2A> properties with an empty `string`.
trans-unit.target: 기본 생성자는 초기화는 <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper.ToolName%2A>, <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper.AssemblyName%2A>, <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper.BitmapName%2A>, 및 <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper.DisplayName%2A> 속성은 빈 `string`합니다.

trans-unit.source: The type of the tool.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper" /> class with the type of the tool.
trans-unit.target: 도구의 형식을 사용하여 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper" /> 클래스의 새 인스턴스를 초기화합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper.ToolName%2A> and <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper.AssemblyName%2A> properties can be extracted from the `toolType` parameter.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper.ToolName%2A> 및 <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper.AssemblyName%2A> 속성은 `toolType` 매개 변수에서 추출할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper.BitmapName%2A> and <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper.DisplayName%2A> properties are each initialized with an empty `string`.
The type of the tool.
The name of the display.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper" /> class with the type of the tool and a specified display name.
trans-unit.target: 도구의 형식 및 지정된 표시 이름을 사용하여 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper" /> 클래스의 새 인스턴스를 초기화합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper.ToolName%2A> and <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper.AssemblyName%2A> properties can be extracted from the `toolType` parameter.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper.ToolName%2A> 및 <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper.AssemblyName%2A> 속성은 `toolType` 매개 변수에서 추출할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper.BitmapName%2A> property is initialized with an empty `string`.
The type of the tool.
A <see langword="string" /> that contains the name of the bitmap.
A <see langword="string" /> that contains the name of the display.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper" /> class with the type of the tool and specified names for the bitmap and display.
trans-unit.target: 도구의 형식과 비트맵 및 표시에 대한 지정된 이름을 사용하여 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper" /> 클래스의 새 인스턴스를 초기화합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper.ToolName%2A> and <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper.AssemblyName%2A> properties can be extracted from the `toolType` parameter.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper.ToolName%2A> 및 <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper.AssemblyName%2A> 속성은 `toolType` 매개 변수에서 추출할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The name of the tool.
The name of the assembly.
The name of the bitmap.
The name of the display.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper" /> class with specified names for the tool, assembly, bitmap, and display.
trans-unit.target: 도구, 어셈블리, 비트맵 및 표시에 대해 지정된 이름을 사용하여 <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper" /> 클래스의 새 인스턴스를 초기화합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the assembly name for the toolbox item.
trans-unit.target: 도구 상자 항목에 대한 어셈블리 이름을 가져오거나 설정합니다.

trans-unit.source: The assembly name.
If the assembly name is changed, an event is raised to indicate that the property value has been changed.
trans-unit.target: 어셈블리 이름이 변경되면 속성 값이 변경되었음을 알리는 이벤트가 발생합니다.

trans-unit.source: The set operation is idempotent: if the assembly name is set to a value that it already has, there is no change.
trans-unit.target: 설정 작업은 idempotent이므로 어셈블리 이름을 이미 있는 값으로 설정하는 경우 변경이 수행되지 않습니다.

trans-unit.source: The assembly name has already been specified and cannot be changed after the corresponding <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Desigen.ToolboxItem" /> has been initialized.
trans-unit.target: 어셈블리 이름이 이미 지정되었고 해당 <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Desigen.ToolboxItem" />이 초기화된 후 변경할 수 없는 경우

trans-unit.source: Gets the bitmap associated with the <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem" /> wrapped by the current object.
trans-unit.target: 현재 개체에 의해 래핑된 <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem" />과 연결된 비트맵을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns a <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Bitmap" /> that is associated with the <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem" />.
Gets or sets the bitmap name.
The bitmap name.
If the bitmap name is changed, an event is raised to indicate that the property value has been changed.
trans-unit.target: 비트맵 이름이 변경되면 속성 값이 변경되었음을 알리는 이벤트가 발생합니다.

trans-unit.source: The set operation is idempotent: if the assembly name is set to a value that it already has, there is no change.
trans-unit.target: 설정 작업은 idempotent이므로 어셈블리 이름을 이미 있는 값으로 설정하는 경우 변경이 수행되지 않습니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the display name.
The display name.
If the display name is changed, an event is raised to indicate that the property has been changed.
trans-unit.target: 표시 이름이 변경되면 속성이 변경되었음을 알리는 이벤트가 발생합니다.

trans-unit.source: The set operation is idempotent: if the assembly name is set to a value that it already has, there is no change.
trans-unit.target: 설정 작업은 idempotent이므로 어셈블리 이름을 이미 있는 값으로 설정하는 경우 변경이 수행되지 않습니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether this <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem" /> is valid.
trans-unit.target: 이 <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem" />이 유효한지 여부를 나타내는 값을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem" /> is valid; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
The <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem> is valid if it is not `null`.
An event that occurs when a property is changed.

The <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper.PropertyChanged> property is defined by the <xref:System.ComponentModel.INotifyPropertyChanged> interface that is implemented by the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper> class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper.PropertyChanged> 속성은 <xref:System.ComponentModel.INotifyPropertyChanged> 클래스에 의해 구현되는 <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper> 인터페이스에 의해 정의됩니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of the tool.
The tool name.
If the name of the tool is changed, an event is raised to indicate that the property value has been changed.
trans-unit.target: 도구의 이름이 변경되면 속성 값이 변경되었음을 알리는 이벤트가 발생합니다.

trans-unit.source: The set operation is idempotent: if the assembly name is set to a value that it already has, there is no change.
trans-unit.target: 설정 작업은 idempotent이므로 어셈블리 이름을 이미 있는 값으로 설정하는 경우 변경이 수행되지 않습니다.

trans-unit.source: The name of the tool cannot be changed after the corresponding <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Desigen.ToolboxItem" /> has been initialized.
trans-unit.target: 해당하는 <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Desigen.ToolboxItem" />이 초기화된 후 도구 이름을 변경할 수 없는 경우

trans-unit.source: Returns a <see langword="string" /> that represents the current object.

Returns the value of the <see cref="P:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper.ToolName" /> property for the current <see cref="T:System.Activities.Presentation.Toolbox.ToolboxItemWrapper" /> object.
Gets the type of the <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem" />.
Returns <see cref="T:System.Type" />.
